==Sharing==
[[File:Gallery_Photo&SharingExample.webp|200px|thumb|A photo inside a sharing pedestal.]]
VRC+ users can share photos, prints, emoji, stickers, and UI themes with other VRC+ within the same instance. Pressing the share button on the respective content type allows the user to drop a [[Sharing|sharing]] pedestal.

== Bundles & Packs ==
Bundles & Packs are how content gets delivered to users. They appear in the Bundles & Packs tab, and once claimed, users will get rewarded with one or multiple of the content types. If users have multiple bundles or packs in their inventory, they can choose which one they want to open by clicking the arrow on either side of the menu.

Bundles & Packs can have an expiry date, in which users must claim before a certain date.

